{"actor":"Dream","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-04-11T12:56:09Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":17,"issue_id":"vex-chat-72h","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"vex-chat-72h\",\"title\":\"Fix bootstrap.sh: declare yq in mise.toml and enable experimental hooks\",\"description\":\"Bootstrap fails because (1) the mise android-sdk plugin needs yq on PATH to parse its metadata, and (2) the postinstall hook requires mise experimental=true. Make bootstrap reproducible by declaring yq as a project mise tool and installing it before the full mise install.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"33427880+dream9x@users.noreply.github.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-11T16:56:03Z\",\"created_by\":\"Dream\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-11T16:56:03Z\"}"}
